SUMMARY:Speed Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Are you anxious about being on a big boat with a bunch of strangers? What if they WEREN'T strangers - but the friends in this friendSHIP! FRIENDSHIP ASSEMBLE! Speed Meeting is a facilitated and casually structured event that allows you to cross that barrier and meet new people! This is a drop-in\, drop-out event. Come whenever you can\, leave when you need to!
CATEGORIES:SHADOW CRUISE
