SUMMARY:Collaborative Mural Creation Begins
DESCRIPTION:All are welcome in this collaborative art piece to create a giant wall mural over the course of the cruise. Each day we'll add more pages onto the mural\, creating a larger and more robust canvas for everyone to build on and add to their previous day's work. At the end of the cruise\, we'll have a final\, Glorious (we hope) product! Artists and non artists are invited to come add their creativity to this project! The mural is located on the forward wall of the Atrium on Deck 2.
CATEGORIES:GAMING
LOCATION:Atrium\, Deck 1\, Midship
