SUMMARY:Nighttime Quiet Zone
DESCRIPTION:The starboard side of the Lido Marketplace will be designated the "quiet side" after 9 pm. Other than at the designated 24/7 gaming tables in the aft section\, no gaming\, no meetings\, no loud noises\, please. Take yer excessive noise over to the port side\, please—or to the back deck\, where the late-night pizza is!
CATEGORIES:GENERAL INFO
LOCATION:Lido Market\, Deck 9\, Aft
SEQUENCE:0
