BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260307T180259Z
DTSTART:20260322T043000Z
DTEND:20260322T053000Z
SUMMARY:Tatbletop RPG Jamboree!
DESCRIPTION:Calling all TTRPG enthusiasts! We're all gonna be on a boat for a lot of hours\, and what better way to while those away than to scheme\, trick\, murder and rampage through a (hopefully) fictional adventure?! The Tabletop Jamboree is a meetup where all TTRPG lovers can meet one another and set up games to play throughout the cruise. We've set up this time and space for everyone looking to RUN a campaign to pitch their session to potential victims players!. If you are looking to GM a campaign and want to get players\, come to this! If you are a player and would love to take part in a TTRPG\, come hear some pitches and join up!
CATEGORIES:GAMING
LOCATION:Ocean Bar\, Deck 3\, Midship
SEQUENCE:0
UID:0d922ef6a8fed3bd73ecbbe437dafb95
URL:http://jococruise2026.sched.com/event/0d922ef6a8fed3bd73ecbbe437dafb95
