SUMMARY:Byzantine Chain Mail Rainbow Bracelet
DESCRIPTION:Learn the classic Byzantine weave and create a colorful bracelet. This beginner friendly class will teach you foundational chain mail skills. The Byzantine pattern is a beautiful\, sturdy weave that's perfect for jewelry and can be applied to countless other projects. No experience necessary and all tools and materials are supplied. Please bring glasses or magnifier if needed for close up work.
