SUMMARY:Craft a Clay Gnome
DESCRIPTION:"oin Clay Artist Laura Parcel and learn how to sculpt your own polymer clay gnome. Class will include instruction on sculpting and constructing a basic gnome and then participants can sculpt simple accessories like clothes\, hats\, and more. Will your gnome be a boat captain? Or maybe a Pirate? Perhaps a Mergnome? Flower Pot Protector? It’s time for a “Choose Your Gnome Adventure”! Gnomes will be 1.5-2 inches tall and will be cured onboard. Info on pickup details provided in class. Participants arriving in the final 30 min of classtime may not have sufficient time to complete a gnome\; work cannot be continued after class concludes. Participants aged 12 and up required.
