SUMMARY:Turkish Fold Maps
DESCRIPTION:Learn to fold and glue a map into a cover\, then personalize it with drawing\, coloring\, and stamping. Map making predates written history and has been independently invented by cultures worldwide. In this class\, you'll creating your own personalized keepsake. What You'll Get: - Two pre-printed maps (illustrated cruise route map & coastline) - Two Covers - 40-page zine with instructions for making your own illustrated maps - Bone Folder - Pen and Pencil The Craft Room has additional coloring supplies when classes are not in session. You may also decorate using Passporto stamps hidden around the ship.
