SUMMARY:Anti-Gravity Derby
DESCRIPTION:This year we’re challenging all engineers\, artists\, safety-conscious daredevils\, and anyone else who likes fun to construct a paper aircraft that will stay afloat as long as possible. Because the last one to hit the Atrium floor WINS! Kudos and prizes* will also be awarded for Artistic Merit\, and/or Ingenuity. Plus other fun surprises (tbd). To participate\, meet Coach Cruise (Storm) and Cruise Mom (Thera) in the Ocean Bar (Deck 3\, Midship) with your aircraft ready to waft. Those wishing to witness the spectacle are encouraged to go to the Deck 2 Atrium area\, or Deck 1 just outside of the central Atrium. *Kudos and Prizes is the name of Storm and Thera’s stage magic act
CATEGORIES:GAMING
LOCATION:Atrium\, Deck 1\, Midship
