SUMMARY:Theme: Villains Day
DESCRIPTION:It’s the day to give the villains their due. They’re not evil\, they’re just misunderstood! (Okay\, some might be evil. Still.) And villains have the most fun and get the best songs! Mad scientists\, dark wizards\, angry cryptids\, conniving minions\, megalomaniacal plumbers’ relatives\, whatever. Today any baddie is a goodie. (We ask that you please stick with fictional villains. The real life villains don’t deserve our attention!)
