SUMMARY:Exploring Queer Desire
DESCRIPTION:Queer Desire is the ability to know the innermost wants and desires of the body/soma and to communicate those desires to partners and loved ones. Somatic exercises will be offered and facilitated by Mischa Gilraen\, creatrix of AuthenticQueerDesires.com. Note: this event will include open\, frank and judgment-free discussions of eros and sexuality and will also include an opt-in somatic practice where participants will have the opportunity to practice giving and receiving by making requests and offers for touch exchange that is non-sexual and non-erotic. Note: this event will include open\, frank and judgment-free discussions of sex- and sexual-related topics\, and also an opt-in somatic practice where participants will have the opportunity to engage in touch exchange that is non-sexual and non-erotic.
CATEGORIES:SHADOW CRUISE
LOCATION:Hudson Room\, Deck 3\, Forward
