SUMMARY:Pop-Up Choir Rehearsal: Golden (from KPop Demon Hunters)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a friendly and fun session where we'll build a choir: one ship\, one song\, one day (no auditions). If you can hum in the shower\, you're qualified! During this session we'll play some fun singing games and warmups\, practice the song in sections and as a full group\, and discuss the meaning and emotion behind the music. Immediately afterward\, we'll make our way to the Atrium to perform our work for the assembled masses and casually record it to share with each other and the world. For those who like to prepare in advance\, you can find the choral arrangement and learning materials linked to this event\, or in this Google drive. It can be very helpful to listen through a few times\, but it's NOT required. Feel free to just show up\, we'll have printed copies available.
CATEGORIES:GENERAL INFO
LOCATION:Crow's Nest\, Deck 11\, Forward
