SUMMARY:Mosaic Crochet
DESCRIPTION:Already know how to crochet and want to learn a new technique? In this class you will learn how to overlay mosaic crochet in a simple\, quick and fun project- a simplified JoCo icon. All you need to know is hot to do a chain\, single and double crochet and how to work front and back loops. We will teach you the rest! You can bring a small amount of your favorite yarn in 2 contrasting colors and hook to match yarn or yarn and hook will be provided. We will be using 2 20g balls of size 4 weight and a 5mm or 5.5mm hook.
CATEGORIES:WORKSHOP
